law AcuerdoDesechamientoDemanda
authority judicial
enacted 2023-07-28

vocabulary
    verb provide: provide

parties
    Plaintiff: Plaintiff Person, natural person
    CivilJudge: CivilJudge Corp, legal person
    ExecutingAuthorities: ExecutingAuthorities Corp, legal person
    DistrictJudge: DistrictJudge Corp, legal person
    CompetentDistrictJudge: CompetentDistrictJudge Corp, legal person

objects
