article 1 Generated
    fact certification TerritorialIncompetence is present
    fact certification TerritorialJurisdiction is present
    rule IncompetenceDismissalRule
        If certification TerritorialIncompetence is present
        then DistrictJudge must provide AmparoPetition to CompetentDistrictJudge.